HW4 Particle Filter

Copy the contents in src/ to your catkin_ws/src/. Should be able to 'catkin_make'.

----------------------------------------------------
To see the map:
% roslaunch particle_filter map.launch
Open RVIZ and subscribe a map to "map" topic.

src/particle_filter/rviz/ has the config file for rviz visualization.

----------------------------------------------------
To see a test map with initial uniform distribution:
Open RVIZ with the given config file.
% catkin_make
% rosrun particle_filter main_node

Should see something like this in the terminal output:
Opening map file /home/XXXX/catkin_ws/src/particle_filter/data/map/testmap.dat
mapsize_x       10
10
mapsize_y       10
10
resolution      1
1
autoshifted_x   0
0
autoshifted_y   0
0
line count: 17
Loading distance map data from /home/XXXX/catkin_ws/src/particle_filter/data/map/testmap.dat.txt
Finished loading
Num particles: 300

